1. Find the song from YT (or from wherever you whish)

2. Download it here:
https://www.freemake.com/pl/free_video_downloader

3. Convert it here:
https://cloudconvert.com/mp4-to-mp3

4. If the file size if huge, compress it here:
https://www.freeconvert.com/mp3-compressor

5. Name the file as follows:
<song_title>.<performer_or_just_0>.mp3

6. Add an entry do audio_meta.json as follows:
"o!_<song_name>": [
    {
        "file": <file_name_from_step_5>,
        "performer": <Performer name that will be displayed>
    }
],